en_436204_0	The National Police Commission has taken steps to promote 2,891 male and female police constables on the instructions of IGP Pujith Jayasundara.
en_436204_1	Accordingly 1,783 officers have been promoted from Police Constables to Sergeants.
en_436204_2	334 women officers have been promoted from women police constable to women police sergeants.
en_436204_3	553 have been promoted from police sergeants to the sub police inspector posts and 76 women officers have been promoted from women police sergeants to the post of women sub inspectors.
en_436204_4	Apart from these, 145 promotions have been given to police drivers.
